Fix Taunt.  I think when discussing class balance, if everyone was chain-doing -whatever-they-do (ie wizard nuking), the warrior should have to be not missing a taunt to still hold aggro. If classes were really balanced, everyones primary role should generate the same ammount of hate. If one class could hold all aggro all the time, this game would suck. I could just heal (Ima Druid), and buff, and nuke with little worry. This is what it's like with a pally now. No wonder so many complain that so and so can't play their class.<br>
<br>
Consider this, make Pallies hold aggro against undead, and make SK's hold aggro against good type mobs. Make a Warrior hold aggro equally well across all types of MoBs.<br>
<br>
I also think Verant should consider what percentage Warrior/Caster hybrids are. If its 75%/25%, make it that way. A Knight that can group heal better than a Druid, HP buff almost as well as a Cleric, stun like a Chanter, is a little to much caster really.<br>
<br>
SK's are a little  different. I think they are close to being where they need to be. All their spells are pretty gimp. FD is their best utility and thats on a 2 second cast and useless against casters.  Hate generating spells are very nice, especially in an Off-Tank setting.<br>
<br>
Then bring both their damage output to 90% of a warriors. Same with the damage they take, should be about 10% more than warriors. <br>
<br>
Maybe then cap their mana pool lower. Maybe around 1000. They can cast a few times a round but not chain stun and heal while tanking a mob.<br>
<br>
I think the only broken fixture of a Warrior is the Taunt. I can count on less then 10% of my spells failing. A Warrior should have the same chance of landing a taunt.<br>
<br>
My 2cp is make a hybrid 100% of a character, not 97% warrior-50% Cleric.<br>
<br>
Bah, work sucks. Sorry for the long post. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=wolfiechain>wolfie chain </A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://dynamic4.gamespy.com/~bidforpower/forum/images/avatars/0/Dragonball-Z_-_gogeta.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/5/03 10:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2113.topic&index=23>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_ale.gif" align=absmiddle>  cheer!</span><hr size=1> ( Retired )<br>
