<br>
Far to many Warriors think equal aggro control with Knights  is either good enough or the answer to your woes.<br>
<br>
While I find the blood and guts approach refreshing, the simple truth is aggro control is NOT enough. <br>
<br>
The lack of reliable aggro control and Knight's finally being made playable is but a fraction of the problem. <br>
<br>
What is the problem you ask?<br>
<br>
No real upgrades or creativity being applied to Warriors or pure melee for years is the problem.<br>
<br>
Many of you have expressed fears of being turned into a hybrid. While these new abilities may take getting used to enjoy bringing more to a group than being a meatshield?<br>
<br>
Welcome the furture and embrace you're new abilities Warriors<br>
You might be suprised..  <p>Zarraa Voltayre<br>
